    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"272771\">@Andrey Oskin</span>  If I'd known enough - I would have followed your suggestion :-)</p>\n<p>I spent quite some time learning about macros, <a href=\"https://github.com/search?q=MacroTools.jl&amp;type=Repositories\">MacroTools.jl</a> and <a href=\"https://github.com/search?q=Match.jl&amp;type=Repositories\">Match.jl</a>. I also enjoyed watching <a href=\"https://youtu.be/U1VhkcTuXuw\">\"JuliaCon 2020 | Advanced Metaprogramming Tools | Mike Innes\"</a>. </p>\n<div class=\"youtube-video message_inline_image\"><a data-id=\"U1VhkcTuXuw\" href=\"https://youtu.be/U1VhkcTuXuw\"><img src=\"https://uploads.zulipusercontent.net/73b98ffc458147865e5a45ec6b736fa208459d0b/68747470733a2f2f692e7974696d672e636f6d2f76692f553156686b6354755875772f64656661756c742e6a7067\"></a></div><p>The result is that I much better understand what I'm asking for, and what the tools do. Maybe <a href=\"https://julia.mit.edu/Cassette.jl/stable/whycassette.html\">Cassette</a> would do what I want. I wrote something pretty simple - which does the job ( abbreviated):</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Julia\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">function</span> <span class=\"n\">run_identity</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">str</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">evp</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">eval</span> <span class=\"o\">‚àò</span> <span class=\"n\">Meta</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">parse</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">evp</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"@show \"</span> <span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">str</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"k\">end</span>\n\n<span class=\"c\"># pvo=permutationsWithOrder(source-set, tuple-size)</span>\n\n<span class=\"c\"># Associativity by exhaustion - feasible because ùîπ is a small type.</span>\n<span class=\"n\">pr</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"Associativity\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"k\">let</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">comb</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">pwo</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">bools</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">3</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">for</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">c</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"k\">in</span> <span class=\"n\">comb</span>\n        <span class=\"n\">run_identity</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"(</span><span class=\"si\">$a</span><span class=\"s\"> ‚äª </span><span class=\"si\">$b</span><span class=\"s\">) ‚äª </span><span class=\"si\">$c</span><span class=\"s\"> == </span><span class=\"si\">$a</span><span class=\"s\"> ‚äª (</span><span class=\"si\">$b</span><span class=\"s\"> ‚äª </span><span class=\"si\">$c</span><span class=\"s\">)\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">end</span>\n<span class=\"k\">end</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>[...]</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Julia\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">Associativity</span>\n<span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">zero</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">zero</span> <span class=\"o\">==</span> <span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">zero</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">zero</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">true</span>\n<span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">zero</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">one</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"o\">==</span> <span class=\"n\">zero</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">one</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">true</span>\n<span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">zero</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"o\">==</span> <span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">zero</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">one</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">true</span>\n<span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">zero</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">zero</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"o\">==</span> <span class=\"n\">zero</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">zero</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">one</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">true</span>\n<span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">one</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"o\">==</span> <span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">one</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">true</span>\n<span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">zero</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">zero</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">zero</span> <span class=\"o\">==</span> <span class=\"n\">zero</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">zero</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">zero</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">true</span>\n<span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">zero</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">one</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">zero</span> <span class=\"o\">==</span> <span class=\"n\">zero</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">zero</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">true</span>\n<span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">one</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">zero</span> <span class=\"o\">==</span> <span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">zero</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">true</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">Commutativity</span>\n<span class=\"n\">zero</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"o\">==</span> <span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">zero</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">true</span>\n<span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">zero</span> <span class=\"o\">==</span> <span class=\"n\">zero</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">true</span>\n<span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"o\">==</span> <span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">true</span>\n<span class=\"n\">zero</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">zero</span> <span class=\"o\">==</span> <span class=\"n\">zero</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">zero</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">true</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">Self</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">inverting</span>\n<span class=\"n\">zero</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">zero</span> <span class=\"o\">==</span> <span class=\"n\">ùï´</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">true</span>\n<span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"o\">‚äª</span> <span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"o\">==</span> <span class=\"n\">ùï´</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">true</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
